The paper presents a new topology optimization method for solving stress constrained and minimum compliance problems. The method is implemented in MATLAB and is compared to an existing optimality criteria method. The paper is likely to belong to the Mechanical Engineering (cs.ME) and Optimization (cs.Optimization) sub-categories, as it deals with optimization methods for mechanical systems. It may also belong to the Numerical Analysis (cs.NA), Civil Engineering (cs.CE), and Electromagnetics (cs.EM) sub-categories, as these fields also involve optimization methods for physical systems.
